<lb ed="L" n="0323b08"/>也帝王興膺籙受圖順天行誅</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>盥</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL158p0323b0814" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">古玩切音貫以盤水沃洗曰盥</note>。</p></cb:def></entry></cb:div></cb:div>
